22
00:01:54,170 --> 00:01:55,580
The carrot puree is too sweet.

23
00:01:58,050 --> 00:02:00,290
- Mr. He, your coffee.
- Thanks.

24
00:02:00,290 --> 00:02:02,010
By the way, I just got a call.

25
00:02:02,010 --> 00:02:04,130
The Bai's Dried Goods Factory

26
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,200
asked us to liaise with them

27
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,520
about the dried bamboo shoots.

28
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,690
They can supply us with those.

29
00:02:07,690 --> 00:02:08,780
And the price is very reasonable.

30
00:02:13,660 --> 00:02:14,500
Everyone, listen up.

31
00:02:16,460 --> 00:02:18,690
Smoked bamboo shoot fish
is added to the new menu.

32
00:02:19,290 --> 00:02:20,130
Yes, Chef.

33
00:02:20,580 --> 00:02:21,570
- Du.
- Yes.

34
00:02:21,690 --> 00:02:22,780
